data.description: Welcome to this 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom gem! Step inside and you'll be greeted by vaulted ceilings with skylights in the living room, creating an open and airy atmosphere. Complete with a cozy wood burning fireplace and wired surround sound perfect for movie nights and gatherings. You'll find glass french doors leading to the patio flooding the home with natural light. Enjoy the convenience of a built-in bookcase for added storage in the living room.  The master bathroom is a true retreat, featuring dual vanities that provide ample space for getting ready, and a walk-in closet to keep your belongings organized. The Backyard is fully fenced with a privacy fence, offering a safe and private space for outdoor activities and relaxation. The 2 car garage boasts a built in work area with built in shelving perfect for DIY projects or storing your tools and equipment. With its existing features and untapped potential, this home is the perfect canvas awaiting your personal touch! Don't miss your opportunity to transform it into your dream!
